ctxDrawImage(c,g,f,e,d,m,n,o,v,t){Settings['Xray']['e']&&(c['globalAlpha']=Settings['Xray']['o']);if(g['tryLoad']===undefined||g['tryLoad']()===0x1){if(t!==undefined)c['drawImage'](g,f,e,Math['max'](0x1,d),Math['max'](0x1,m),n,o,v,t);else{if(m!==undefined)c['drawImage'](g,f,e,d,m);else c['drawImage'](g,f,e)}}}function draw_info_box(){var c=game['info_box'],g=c['id'];if(c['activated']===0x1&&c['display']===0x1){if(INFO_BOX[g]===undefined)INFO_BOX[g]=create_info_box(g);if(c['craft']===0x1)ctxDrawImage(ctx,INFO_BOX[g],c['x'],c['y']);else{if(c['x']-0x50+INFO_BOX[g]['width']>canw)ctxDrawImage(ctx,INFO_BOX[g],canw-INFO_BOX[g]['width']-0xa,c['y']-INFO_BOX[g]['height']-0xa);else ctxDrawImage(ctx,INFO_BOX[g],c['x']-0x50,c['y']-INFO_BOX[g]['height']-0xa)}}}function draw_slot_number(c,g,f){var e=sprite[SPRITE['SLOT_NUMBER']][c],d=g['info']['translate']['x']+0x5*scale,m=g['info']['translate']['y']+0x5*scale;if(g['info']['state']==BUTTON_CLICK||f)m+=scale*0x5;ctxDrawImage(ctx,e,d,m)}function draw_amount(c,g){if(!sprite[SPRITE['COUNTER']][c])sprite[SPRITE['COUNTER']][c]=create_text(scale,'x'+c,0x11,'#FFF');var f=sprite[SPRITE['COUNTER']][c],e=g['info']['translate']['x']+g['info']['img'][0x0]['width']-f['width']-0xe*scale,d=g['info']['translate']['y']+g['info']['img'][0x0]['height']-f['height']-0x13*scale;if(g['info']['state']==BUTTON_CLICK)d+=scale*0x5;ctxDrawImage(ctx,f,e,d)}function draw_well_inventory(){if(user['chest']['open']||user['furnace']['open']||user['windmill']['open']||user['bread_oven']['open']||user['extractor']['open'])return;user['well']['open']=![];var draw_lava_effect(c,g,f,e,d,m,n,o,v){if(o===undefined)o=0x0;for(var t=n;t>=o;t--){for(var u=c;u<=g;u++){for(var B=f;B<=e;B++){var z=MAP['tiles'][u][B];if(z===undefined||z[m]===undefined)continue;var
